text: Helstrom is an American TV series and that is based on the Marvel Comics characters Daimon and Satana Helstrom. The series was created by Paul Zbyszewski and was released on Hulu on October 16, 2020. The series was produced by Marvel Television. It would originally be part of the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU), but Zbyszewski says it is not.
